{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "牡丹 第2话 做饭也要一心一意！",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "库菈乌！教我做饭吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "做饭吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "我之前不是\\n给大家做了荞麦面吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "啊……那个啊……\\n唔，那个……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "虽然自己来说有点怪，\\n不过说实话那荞麦面真是难吃。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "我不甘心就这样\\n被大家认为自己很不擅长做饭！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "所以拜托你！\\n请教我做饭吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "原来如此，我懂了。\\n交给我吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "那作为练习，\\n你就和我一起做焗饭吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "好的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "首先，把洋葱和土豆切片。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "好的！呀啊啊啊啊啊！\\n呜呜，洋葱熏得眼睛好痛！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "看样子已经切好了。\\n咦？切得太厚了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "咦，是吗？\\n但这样的口感不是更好吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "请再切薄一点，\\n不然很难煮熟。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "唔，这样应该差不多了吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "接下来，把切好的土豆\\n和洋葱炒至断生。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "交给我吧！用大火炒啊炒♪\\n嗯，这样就行了吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "不……炒过头了。\\n已经焦了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "啊……这么一说的确……\\n不过，总比没炒熟好吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "算了……可以想办法用调味来补救，\\n姑且就这样吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "关火，加入面粉和黄油\\n搅拌均匀。量的话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "这样够了吧？嘿！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "太多了！\\n得好好控制量才行。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "啊？大致目测一下\\n不就行了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "唉……我知道你为什么不擅长做饭了。\\n因为你太粗枝大叶了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "粗枝大叶？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "只要照着菜谱做，\\n一定能做得好吃。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "之所以会失败，\\n都是“大概”、“凭感觉”\\n这种不按菜谱的做法造成的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "但是，菜谱上写的量和时间之类的\\n要求都很细致，不觉得麻烦吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "菜谱是基础中的基础。\\n你觉得不打好基础能进步吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "呜，的确……\\n无力反驳。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "那就再做一次吧。\\n这次要严格按照菜谱来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "就这样，\\n牡丹接受了库菈乌的严格指导。\\n结果……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "终于做好了！怎、怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我嚼……嗯。\\n按照菜谱做果然很好吃。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "太好了！我终于能做得好吃了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你的悟性很高，\\n只要好好按照菜谱做，\\n什么菜都能做好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "真的吗！？那么，\\n有件事想跟你商量……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "什么？\\n今天的晚饭由牡丹负责？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "没错！为了一雪前耻！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂喂，真的假的。\\n那个荞麦面的噩梦又要卷土重来？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "哼哼哼。放心吧，\\n现在的我已经脱胎换骨了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我把拿手菜式都教给她了，\\n只要按照食谱做就不会失败。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "我可不会重蹈覆辙，\\n一定会做出美味的饭菜！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好，我很期待哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "各位就尽管期待\\n今天的晚饭吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "真的没问题吗？\\n还是库菈乌去盯着点……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "她说想独自完成，\\n不然就不算是一雪前耻了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "别担心。\\n只要牡丹想做，她是可以做到的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "也是……那我们一起去\\n特训一下，把肚子空出来吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几小时后……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呼，出了好多汗。\\n肚子都饿扁了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "已经到晚饭时间了。\\n哎呀，好香啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "唔！欢迎回来！\\n那个，关于晚饭……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "噢！桌上有汤。\\n看上去很好喝。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "呃……那个……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "凉了就不好喝了，\\n我们赶快喝吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那我不客气了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯……好喝！\\n好期待其它饭菜啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "说起来，怎么没看到别的菜呢。\\n等下才拿出来吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "不……\\n这就是今天的晚饭了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "啊？难道只有汤吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "对不起！真的只有汤！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "咦！？除了汤，我还教了你别的吧？\\n到底发生了什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "那个……我先做的是汤。\\n按照菜谱准备好之后，\\n严格控制了量，也注意了火候。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "我把其它菜放在锅里预备，\\n先集中精力煮汤，\\n结果……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "等汤做好了，\\n其他锅里的菜都煮沸溢光了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "因为太专注于某件事\\n疏忽了其它吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "我没脸见人了！\\n真想在地上挖个洞钻进去！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我忘了以你的性格\\n是没法一心多用的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "下次我会教你安排好各个步骤，\\n所以别太沮丧了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "呜呜……谢谢你，库菈乌。\\n今天失败的料理，\\n我、我会负起责任……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "等一下，牡丹！你不用那么做！\\n统统由我来吃掉！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110312_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牡丹",
            "context": "咦，兰扎卜……\\n你……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "现在应该会觉得好吃！\\n因为饥饿是最好的调味料！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "太好了呢……牡丹。\\n再怎么失败都有人帮忙处理掉，\\n所以你就放心吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}